    <string name="whats_new_title">New in version %s</string>
    <string name="whats_new_text">
        - Fixed changing from summer time to normal time.\n
        - Added GPS as an alternate location provider.\n
        - User can save the current location as a fixed position.\n
        - Added reset zoom to the context menu.\n
        - Improved layout to support Android tablets.\n
        - Added ads to support the development of this application.
        Ads can be disabled from the preferences.
    </string>

